<div class="Title">
<h1>菅氏、総裁選立候補を正式表明 「持てる力全て尽くす」</h1>
</div>
<div class="ArticleInfo"><p class="UpdateDate"><time datetime="2020-09-02T17:40+09:00">2020/9/2 17:40</time></p>
</div></div><!--ArticleTitle END-->
<div class="ThmbPhotoArea">
<div class="ThmbPhotoBox">
